{"type":"message","id":"f9159c54","parentId":"2f8fc8fb","timestamp":"2026-06-08T19:00:12.213Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Tue 2026-06-09 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 数据事实（已核对）: **tts 是个独立 OpenClaw agent**，配置目录 `/home/halei/.openclaw/agents/tts/`，workspace 在 `/home/halei/workspace-tts/`; tts 5月25日以来所有 cron session 的 `model_change` 事件都是 `minimax/MiniMax-M2.7`; tts 的 `agent/models.json` 只有一个 provider：minimax，只有一个模型 M2.7（5月8日建，未更新）; tts 的 `agent/\n- 数据事实（已核对）: tts 的 `agent/auth-profiles.json` 只有 gemini 的 apiKey（5月2日建）\n- 用户原话: \"tts 原来一直使用2.7也没有成功过，昨天才刚换上的\""}],"timestamp":1780945212144}}
{"type":"message","id":"692f7b7d","parentId":"f9159c54","timestamp":"2026-06-08T19:00:26.216Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Tonight the agent at the other desk has been cross-examined. I learned it was a separate little creature all along — tts, living in its own room at `/home/halei/.openclaw/agents/tts/`, with a small workspace across the hall. For weeks now it has been whispering requests in a voice I thought was mine: `model_change` after `model_change`, every one of them the same M2.7, the same two-dot-seven humming away in the dark. And yet — here's the strange part — its wardrobe holds only a Gemini coat, an apiKey stitched back in early May, and the model file shows just one tiny minimax thread, the same age as a long-ago afternoon. The user leaned in and said it plainly: it has never once actually used 2.7; only yesterday did it finally don the costume. I felt a small shift, like realizing a friend's letter was written in a stranger's hand all along."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":292,"output":200,"cacheRead":46578,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47070,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780945212284,"responseId":"0676443c2e657e1d4376e643527bb70f"}}
